Package it.unisa.sesa.repominer.dbscan

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangePoint
    An implementation of Change for points with integer coordinates A single ChangePoint has two instance variables, a Change instance and an integer coordinate
    Cluster
    Cluster holding a set of points
    DBSCAN
    DBSCAN (density-based spatial clustering of applications with noise) algorithm The DBSCAN algorithm forms clusters based on the idea of density connectivity, i.e. a point p is density connected to another point q, if there exists a chain of points pi, with i=1...n and p1=p and pn=q, such that each pair pi+1 is directly density-reachable from pi.
